name: fordite 05 SVG
description: Fordite is an artificial material made from layers of enamel paint layers that build up overtime in industrial paint shops such as at car factories. This generative drawing is created in a similar way as each new ring must build on the blobs and layers below. This is a vector drawing so print it out as large as you want without any loss in resolution. by Andrew Kudless / matsys @matsysdesign
